-sV:  get services version
-O: get OS

-sn:  disable ports scan, discover host only

-iL:  a txt with hosts to scan

-Pn:  disable ICMP; assume host alive, go scan ports
-PE:  send ICMP, after ARP
--disable-arp-ping:  disable ARP; can do with -Pn

--packet-trace:  show all send and received packets

--reason:  show reason for result

default = top 1000 ports
-F:  top 100 ports
--top-ports=10:  top 10 ports
-p-:  all ports

-p:  specify ports

-n:  disable DNS

-sS:  do TCP 2 shake
-sT:  do TCP 3 shake
-sU:  do UDP
-sA:  send ACK packet to bypass firewall, as firewall may block SYN from external, but can't tell whetehr ACK from internal or external

-v: show verbose
--stats-every=5s: show status every 5 seconds

-sC:  use default scripts
--script:  use specified scripts
--script discovery:  use discovery category scripts
--script vuln:  use vuln category scripts
-A:  aggresive scane

-T 5: insane timing template; defaults is 3

--initial-rtt-timeout 50ms --max-rtt-timeout 100ms:  rtt too low may overlook hosts
--max-retries 0:  1 try only; default is 10
--min-rate 300:  send 300 packets per second

-D RND:5  :  place true IP into 5 random decoy IPs
-S:  mannully specified a IP
-g 53  :  specified 53 as source port
--dns-server:  specified a DNS; DNSs in DMZ is better


offical mannual:
  https://nmap.org/book/toc.html
  https://nmap.org/book/man-port-scanning-techniques.html


sudo nc -s LocalIP -p53 TargetIP 50000:  sudo为了提权，因为1024以下端口需要系统权限;  -s 为了解决端口冲突，不用-s的话，默认0.0.0.0，使用所有网卡的53端口，一般被dns服务占用
